 cross section. In addition, the data on the 430 keV\nresonance in 15N(p, \\alpha \\gamma)12C may be useful for hydrogen depth\nprofiling.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 11 May 2010 16:01:05 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 1 Jun 2010 08:32:18 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-03-17"}
