 as well as a clearer indication of\nthe binary's fate once contact is reached.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 12 May 2010 00:49:47 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 21 May 2010 18:39:37 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-05-18"}
